frames.caption: A luminous lion constellation is depicted against a starry night sky, with its body formed by glowing lines and points of light. The lion appears majestic and dynamic, as if leaping through the cosmos, surrounded by a celestial backdrop.
frames.description: The scene illustrates a cosmic representation of a lion constellation, set in a vast and star-filled universe. The lion is composed of bright, interconnected lines and dots, creating a striking visual against the dark, expansive space.

frames.caption: A majestic figure stands adorned in ornate golden armor, featuring intricate lion motifs. Their long, flowing blonde hair cascades around a regal crown, set against a starry cosmic backdrop.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy character in a celestial setting, exuding power and nobility. The figure's armor is richly detailed, emphasizing themes of strength and royalty.
